// Per-developer Xcode signing — NOT committed (Local.xcconfig is gitignored).
//
//   cp Local.xcconfig.example Local.xcconfig   # then fill in your team id
//
// Find your team id: Xcode → Settings → Accounts → select your Apple ID →
// your team's ID is shown in the team list (e.g. "Dacheng Chen (Personal Team)"
// → a 10-char id like AB12CD34EF).
//
// Set the team HERE, not in Xcode's Signing & Capabilities tab — picking a
// team there writes it into project.pbxproj, which is shared and would break
// signing for everyone else.
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID
